# React Hooks Dependency Discipline

Use this ESLint fragment:

```json
{
  "plugins": ["react", "react-hooks"],
  "rules": {
    "react-hooks/exhaustive-deps": "error"
  }
}
```

## Example

```tsx
useEffect(() => {
  fetchData(userId);
}, [userId, fetchData]);
```
